scene.message:
Night Queen's Voice: Grr...{wait_fr:30}{nl}
To be beaten by brats{nl}
like these{wait_fr:30}{nl}
how vexing...{waitkey}{clearbox}But know this well.{waitkey}{clearbox}So long as the human heart{nl}
can turn hope into despair,{nl}
the "Eternal Night" will come{nl}
again and again...{waitkey}{ret}

Masked Girl: No...{wait_fr:30}{nl}
Why?{wait_fr:30}{nl}
This is my world, and yet...{waitkey}{ret}

Masked Boy: Just as I thought.{nl}
A hastily borrowed edge{nl}
won't cut it after all.{waitkey}{clearbox}We'll have to handle{nl}
things ourselves.{waitkey}{clearbox}{ctl0f:1}{wait_fr:30}, was it?{nl}
It seems you and I{nl}
will meet again.{waitkey}{ret}
